playcanvasConfigJson.title: PlayCan Config JSON
playcanvasConfigJson.description: testConfig.json in the base folder - Change your settings in this file for test modes

playcanvasTestMode.title: Playcanvas Test Mode
playcanvasTestMode.description: Test Mode for playcanvas, tested update

motionThreshold.title: Motion Threshold
motionThreshold.description: Number of meters moved in one frame before CCD is enabled

sweptSphereRadius.title: Swept Sphere Radius
sweptSphereRadius.description: This should be below the half extent of the collision volume. E.g For an object of dimensions 1 meter, try 0.2

renderLine.title: Render Line
renderLine.description: If checked the line will be rendered in scene (works both in editor and on launch).

renderColor.title: Render Color
renderColor.description: The color of the line to render.

renderStep.title: Render Step
renderStep.description: The length of each line segment rendered.

curveType.title: Curve Type
curveType.description: The type of the line curve rendered.

isStatic.title: Is Static
isStatic.description: If checked the line will not update if any point gets updated (performance optimization).

animationEntity.title: Animation Entity
animationEntity.description: The entity to animate on the path.

loopAnimation.title: Loop Animation
loopAnimation.description: If selected the animation will loop infinitely.

yoyoAnimation.title: Yoyo Animation
yoyoAnimation.description: If selected and Loop Animation is also selected the animation will yoyo back when looping.

autoplay.title: Auto Play
autoplay.description: If selected the animation will automatically start when this entity is initialized.
